room_title: Escape room "Escape from One-Eyed Jack" by Cannon Beach Escape Room in Cannon Beach
room_address: 248 N Spruce St, Cannon Beach, OR 97110
room_description: You've been kidnapped by One-Eyed Jack – the most evil pirate in the Pacific. One-Eyed Jack has locked you in his captain’s quarters and will make you walk the plank at dawn… which is just an hour away. But there is hope. A rogue pirate hid a series of clues that lead to a way out. Can you solve them? Or are you destined to spend the rest of your days in Davy Jones’ locker?
